# Ship Pipeline

1. Rebase on base branch
2. Run full test suite
3. Audit coverage and scope drift
4. Pre-landing code review (6-point checklist)
5. Bisectable commits (one logical change per commit)
6. Verification gate — all tests pass
7. Push and open PR
8. Never ship from main/master directly
